					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you want a <em>cryptographic</em> hash, neither CRC32 nor adler32 are suitable.<br /><br />If you don't want a cryptographic hash, you don't need to worry about byte shuffling. That isn't the kind of failure mode that will come from save RAM corruption.</div>

